junit group:

JUNIT was introduced in your company.
What effect did it have on the project 
duration ? 

  o longer duration (with better quality) 
  o no change in duration 
  o reduction of duration 
  o benefit after first attempt

http://groups.yahoo.com/group/junit/polls

not collected via email. To vote, you must go to the Yahoo! Groups 
web site listed above.

Thanks!
